BRAND — Naked Shop Investors






















































OUR BRAND



our brandNaked was founded on one basic desire: to create a new standard for how products worn close to the skin fit, feel and function. We have spent years developing designs and fabrics that feel like nothing else. Like you are wearing nothing at all. So you feel how you want to feel: free, unencumbered and empowered. We know because that's how we feel when we wear them. We are naked.















































