			Company Description 


			Naked Brand Group, Inc. is engaged in manufacturing and selling of undergarments. It offers intimate apparel products for men including trunks, briefs, boxer briefs, undershirts, t-shirts and lounge pants under the Naked brand. The company was founded on May 17, 2005 and is headquartered in New York...
		


                Naked Brand Group, Inc. is engaged in manufacturing and selling of undergarments. It offers intimate apparel products for men including trunks, briefs, boxer briefs, undershirts, t-shirts and lounge pants under the Naked brand. The company was founded on May 17, 2005 and is headquartered in New York, NY.
            




